{
  "stem": "24195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were sitting in-- every house had, you know, shelters, air-raid shelters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were sitting there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was just-- everything was-- bombs were just raining around us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And practically a whole quarter of the city was on fire with these incendiary bombs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They just-- there's no way to stop them, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Water doesn't put, put them out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You just let it burn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so we have-- get back to the-- to the apartment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Our house-- our building wasn't-- apartment building wasn't, wasn't hit, but pretty much around us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We got a phone call.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it said, come immediately.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He said, the clinic is-- was total direct hit, every-- a lot of casualties.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "No, no, no public transportation-- we were running, walking five miles and-- to the clinic.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And what a picture.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, the whole place is torn down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The emergency crews with, with, you know, big lights-- emergency lights on, digging out the people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this governess, this-- who, who was among the people that were killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She was in the large elevator where they have gurneys trying to pick people-- putting people down from the upper floors when the bomb hit.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that called-- it was a five-story building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The whole shaft fell on top of the large elevator.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Everybody who was in there was, you know, killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And many other people in the hospital were killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That was a night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I put up-- and, and we, we were trying to protect, standing there, because there were people who started stealing immediately, too, you know, when you have a situation like this.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
